eacute;sente la mani&egrave;re de&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpchannel.com/traduire-mu-plugins-wordpress/">traduire une extension dans le dossier mu-plugins</a>.</p>\n<h3>G&eacute;rer une newsletter avec WordPress</h3>\n<p>Manuel <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://ms-studio.net/faq/gerer-une-newsletter-avec-wordpress/">compare diff&eacute;rents outils de newsletters</a>.</p>\n<h3>WordPress Quick and Clean</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9O_bH4SLaUTvfsmuoQeUuStSMu2ua2G7">Une chaine YouTube</a> qui diffuse des&nbsp; mini-tuto sur WordPress.</p>\n<h3>Une app iOS prend exemple sur WordPress</h3>\n<p>Quand une app iOS prend exemple sur WordPress, <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.zdnet.fr/actualites/ios-appsifyme-veut-rendre-le-developpement-d-appli-aussi-simple-que-wordpress-39797687.htm">&ccedil;a donne Appsify.me</a>.</p>\n<h3>Extension : Le dilemme gratuit versus payant</h3>\n<p>Fabrice donne son avis sur le&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpformation.com/plugins-wordpress-gratuits-premium">dilemme entre extension payante et extension gratuite</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=RwYVvd_kKFM:bP6i3ipazT4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=RwYVvd_kKFM:bP6i3ipazT4:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=RwYVvd_kKFM:bP6i3ipazT4:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=RwYVvd_kKFM:bP6i3ipazT4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Wo